class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="戛纳电影节" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cannes-Film-Festival-Photo-by-Sameer-Al-DOUMY-_-AFP-Photo-by-SAMEER-AL-DOUMY_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cannes-Film-Festival-Photo-by-Sameer-Al-DOUMY-_-AFP-Photo-by-SAMEER-AL-DOUMY_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cannes-Film-Festival-Photo-by-Sameer-Al-DOUMY-_-AFP-Photo-by-SAMEER-AL-DOUMY_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cannes-Film-Festival-Photo-by-Sameer-Al-DOUMY-_-AFP-Photo-by-SAMEER-AL-DOUMY_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cannes-Film-Festival-Photo-by-Sameer-Al-DOUMY-_-AFP-Photo-by-SAMEER-AL-DOUMY_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cannes-Film-Festival-Photo-by-Sameer-Al-DOUMY-_-AFP-Photo-by-SAMEER-AL-DOUMY_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>随着戛纳电影节本周开幕，预计有关欧洲娱乐业虐待女性的新指控将被公开。</p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/cannes-movies-best-films-festival-2672567"><b>我们现在应该在戛纳 - 所以这里有电影节有史以来最伟大的 10 部电影</b></a></li></ul><p>关于法国存在“十名男性秘密名单”的传言在法国广为流传，据说其中包括涉嫌虐待女性的主要演员和导演。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/film/article/2024/may/11/secret-list-abusers-cannes-film-festival" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《卫报》</i></a>报道，这份名单被描述为“爆炸性的”，据说是与其他“法国领先的金融公司”一起匿名发送到巴黎国家电影中心的。</p><p> <i>《费加罗报》</i>和<i>《鸭报》</i>都声称，节日组织者在指控公开之前已经成立了危机管理小组。</p><p>周三（5月15日），一部有关行业虐待的短片<em>《Moi Aussi》</em>也将首映，预计它将进一步追究法国艺术界的责任。</p><p>这部电影由朱迪思·戈德雷什 (Judith Godrèche) 制作，她在讲述自己在职业生涯早期遭受的攻击后，被称为法国“#MeToo”大使。</p><p>这部电影收录了许多从事艺术工作的女性的话。 “突然间，我面前出现了一群受害者，这一现实也代表了法国，有来自不同社会背景和各代人的许多故事，”戈德雷什在谈到这篇文章时说道（来自<i>《卫报》）</i> 。 “那么问题是，我要拿它们做什么？当你被所听到的、被大量的证词压垮时，你会怎么做？” </p><figure id="attachment_3756128" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756128" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756128" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Judith-Godreche-GEOFFROY-VAN-DER-HASSELT_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="朱迪思·戈德雷什" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Judith-Godreche-GEOFFROY-VAN-DER-HASSELT_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Judith-Godreche-GEOFFROY-VAN-DER-HASSELT_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Judith-Godreche-GEOFFROY-VAN-DER-HASSELT_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Judith-Godreche-GEOFFROY-VAN-DER-HASSELT_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Judith-Godreche-GEOFFROY-VAN-DER-HASSELT_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Judith-Godreche-GEOFFROY-VAN-DER-HASSELT_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756128" class="wp-caption-text">朱迪思·戈德雷什（Judith Godrèche）——图片来源：GEOFFROY VAN DER HASSELT/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/cannes-festival-criticised-for-supporting-predators-after-johnny-depp-appearance-3444630">克鲁瓦塞特大道上的示威者反对约翰尼·德普在电影节开幕影片<i>《珍妮·杜巴里》</i>中</a>与艾梅柏·希尔德一起受审。德普和赫德之间的冲突始于 2019 年，当时德普<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/johnny-depps-defamation-case-against-amber-heard-is-going-ahead-3022188">起诉赫德诽谤</a>，此前赫德在 2018 年为<i>《华盛顿邮报》</i>撰写了一篇专栏文章，声称她是家庭暴力的受害者。</p><p>这位<i>《海王》</i>女演员随后在次年反诉德普，该案在 2022 年开庭审理后很快成为头条新闻。当年 6 月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/johnny-depp-amber-heard-jury-reaches-verdict-3238472">陪审团得出结论，希尔德在文章中诽谤德普</a>。</p><p>去年 12 月，案件结束时，据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/amber-heard-to-pay-johnny-depp-1million-to-settle-defamation-case-3369211">希尔德将被要求向前夫支付 100 万美元（79.5 万英镑）</a> ，远低于 6 月份她被勒令向德普支付的 835 万美元（664 万英镑）。 。</p><p>在英国诽谤案中，德普被发现对赫德进行了暴力家庭虐待。然而，在美国的案件中，她的说法被证明不属实。</p><p>此前，戛纳电影节主席蒂埃里·弗雷莫<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cannes-director-defends-opening-festival-with-johnny-depp-film-3430487">为自己邀请德普参加的决定进行了辩护。</a></p><p> “我不知道约翰尼·德普在美国的形象如何，”他（通过<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/world-news/2023/05/16/cannes-boss-defends-johnny-depp-festival-didnt-care-heard/"><i>《电讯报</i></a>》）说道。 “说实话，在我的生活中，我只有一条规则，那就是在法律框架内的思想自由、言论自由和行动自由。”</p><p> “如果约翰尼·德普被禁止出演一部电影，或者这部电影被禁止，我们就不会在这里谈论它，”他补充道。 “如果这个世界上有一个人对这一广为人知的审判毫无兴趣，那就是我。我不知道它是关于什么的。我也很关心约翰尼·德普作为演员。” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/russell-brand-faces-further-claims-accused-rape-sexual-assault-3499490"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p><strong>如需有关英国性骚扰、侵犯和强奸的帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问<a href="https://rapecrisis.org.uk/find-a-centre/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，请访问<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RAINN</a> 。</strong></p></div></div><p>即将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-list-of-secret-abusers-set-to-hit-film-industry-at-cannes-3756109">在戛纳电影节冲击电影业的新秘密滥用者名单</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
在 Massive Attack 的支持下，已有 100 多个艺人退出了 2024 年加沙大逃亡抵制活动https://www.nme.com/news/music/over-100-acts-have-now-dropped-out-of-the-great-escape-2024-in-gaza-boycott-with-support-from-大规模攻击-3756090？utm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign =超过100个行为现在已经放弃了2024年大逃亡，在加沙抵制，并有来自大规模的支持攻击Tom SkinnerTue, 14 May 2024 14:13:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsNME RadarIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3756090 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Massive Attack 乐队的 Robert &quot;3D&quot; Del Naja（左）和 Alfie Templeman（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>阿尔菲·坦普尔曼说：“我的道德不能也不会与娱乐和人类苦难的融合相一致。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/over-100-acts-have-now-dropped-out-of-the-great-escape-2024-in-gaza-boycott-with-support-from-massive-attack-3756090">在 Massive Attack 的支持下，超过 100 名艺人已退出《2024 年加沙大逃亡》抵制活动，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Massive Attack 乐队的 Robert &quot;3D&quot; Del Naja（左）和 Alfie Templeman（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>为了声援巴勒斯坦，已有超过 100 名艺人退出今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/the-great-escape">大逃亡音乐节</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack</a>也公开支持抵制活动。</p><p> 2024 年的该活动将展示新晋艺术家，将于明天（5 月 15 日）至周六（18 日）在布莱顿的各个音乐场馆举行。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="71"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-10-best-new-artists-the-great-escape-2023-radar-3443679"><b>我们在 2023 年大逃亡中看到的 10 个最佳新表演</b></a></li></ul><p>“大逃亡”由巴克莱银行赞助，由于该银行对向以色列供应武器的公司进行金融投资，巴克莱银行在加沙持续冲突中一直引起争议。</p><p>这个问题首先在发起人 How To Catch A Pig 和 The Menstrual Cramps 乐队发起的请愿书中得到强调，此后签名的音乐家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alfie-templeman">Alfie Templeman</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lip-critic">Lip Critic</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mary-in-the-junkyard">Mary In The Junkyard</a> 。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cherym-pull-out-of-the-great-escape-festival-due-to-its-links-with-barclays-bank-3617202">由于音乐节与巴克莱银行的联系，Cherym 退出了 The Great Escape</a> ，之后唱片公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cherym-pull-out-of-the-great-escape-festival-due-to-its-links-with-barclays-bank-3617202">Alcopop 和 Big Scary Monsters 也</a>加入了抵制并退出了该活动。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dozens-more-artists-join-great-escape-2024-boycott-as-half-the-line-up-demands-festival-drop-barclays-sponsor-in-solidarity-with-palestine-3619074">很快，又有数十个表演团体纷纷效仿</a>，其中超过一半的表演团体要求 The Great Escape 放弃与巴克莱银行的赞助协议。</p><p>在谈到不参加音乐节的决定时，兰布里尼女孩表示：“我们今年不会参加大逃亡音乐节。考虑到巴克莱的赞助，这是一种有针对性的文化抵制方式。</p><p> “巴克莱银行向向以色列国防军提供军事技术和武器的公司提供超过 10 亿英镑的金融服务，从而使加沙地带的恐怖现象长期存在。”</p><p>现在，共有 106 名艺术家取消了原定在 2024 年大逃亡中的演出，约占全部节目的四分之一。根据一份新闻稿，他们将电影节与巴克莱银行的合作伙伴关系“资助种族灭绝”作为退出的理由。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C66pOrgteOZ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg wid